==Agincourt today==
[[File:Agincourt Memorial.jpg|thumb|right|Agincourt Memorial]]
[[File:Agincourt archers memorial.jpg|thumb|A list of English archers killed at Agincourt, as recorded in the village's museum]]
There is a modern museum in Agincourt village dedicated to the battle.<ref>[http://illucolor.fr/7_vallees_comm/Azincourt/index.html Agincourt Museum]</ref> The museum lists the names of combatants of both sides who died in the battle.

